Developer Terms of Use
des: Take Pilates classes with Alexa. All you need to get started is a Pilates mat and about 10-20 minutes of your time. You don't need any equipment for these classes. The classes are primarily based on the classical Pilates mat sequences. Alexa knows a variety of Pilates sequences, so it won’t get boring. Say ‘Alexa, start pilates class’, and let Alexa guide you through an enjoyable Pilates experience. To learn more about Pilates exercises and take a variety of Pilates classes, visit ALotOfPilates.com
